title: Clone a Pipeline in Jenkins
tags: @zettel _method jenkins
roam-id: 426b7685-1e08-479f-b612-8204e60cc17f
type: text/markdown

- click "new item"
- enter a new name for the item
- at the end of the page there will be a section called **"Copy From"**
- enter the pipeline name you want to clone
- click OK
